Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:27.69,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}何百回でも遮るモノに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:31.16,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}翳してみせる僕の願い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:33.90,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}必ず君に伝える日まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:38.45,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}正しさは譲れないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:41.53,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}進み続けてゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:44.16,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}何度でも 彷徨いながら目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:49.71,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}いつか黎明の元へ 帰る時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:54.84,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}痛む泥濘の中で 祈りを描くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:00.09,OP-Jp2,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0CA7E5&\blur17\t(0,300,\blur2\c&HFFFFFF&)}心配ないと 言い聞かせながら
